{"tid":2256780,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"律政司翻舊帳 6年後追收黃之鋒佔旺案訟費逾8萬元","createTime":"2020-10-24T15:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T22:40:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4cf9ca5e19dff86b8e6d8d5a82c51807bda6dcfa","tid":2256780,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:36:57.000Z","msg":"2014年雨傘運動期間，時任學民思潮召集人黃之鋒被指違反禁制令，阻撓執達主任於旺角清場，被控藐視法庭，2019年被判監兩個月。黃原獲法援署批出申請，支付訴訟等費用，但律政司於今年8月去信他，表示法援並不包括所有聆訊的法律費用，向他索取84,127.67元。黃之鋒表示，同案部份被告亦被追收費用，批評律政司6年後翻舊帳相當荒謬，對欠款感到一頭霧水，正交由律師跟進。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒指，政治起訴長年累月消耗被告的時間、精神與體力，更有金錢上的壓力，「2014年被起訴的案件，竟然會在6年以後突然追討費用，實在相當荒謬」。律政司於8月17日的來信中提及，追討訟費的金額是於今年5月在未經聆訊下決定，一共為84,127.67元，當中以律師費佔最多，為71,475.67元，其餘為律師代墊付費用和稅項等，要求黃在7日內回覆和確認欠款，否則會頒佈有關命令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201024/4XXY4QC5INCR5KXOZPPXYCDGXM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201024%2F4XXY4QC5INCR5KXOZPPXYCDGXM%2F&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=8c1bc089\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201024%2F4XXY4QC5INCR5KXOZPPXYCDGXM%2F&h=f77ef2bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201024/4XXY4QC5INCR5KXOZPPXYCDGXM/</a>"},{"pid":"0186a298ce113a9ea73e93a233db906240a2b9f8","tid":2256780,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ecc9dab4ba67f9ec53255be21e79c42be1347d","tid":2256780,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:39:50.000Z","msg":"逐蚊交囉"},{"pid":"a6837a05960858842bf3f04bbc4f3d09c438595f","tid":2256780,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0186a298ce113a9ea73e93a233db906240a2b9f8","tid":2256780